<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM1.1.3">
<l>pēṇic cīruṭaip piḷḷai piṟantiṉil</l>
<l>kāṇat tāmpuku vārpukkup pōtuvā</l>
<l>rāṇop pārivaṉ nērillai kāṇṭiru</l>
<l>vōṇat tāṉula kāḷumeṉ pārkaḷē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>When, having been wished for, the child who possesses good qualities was born,</l>
<l>those who entered to see him, entered and left saying,</l>
<l>“this one is not like [other] men with virtue, see!</l>
<l>He whose [asterism is] Tiruvōṇa rules the world”</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
